Sri Lanka Wins Toss, Decides to Bat in First Test With England in Cardiff

-- B y   C h r i s   E l s e r
-- 
2011-05-26T13:28:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/sri-lanka-wins-toss-decides-to-bat-in-first-test-with-england-in-cardiff.html
Sri Lanka  won the toss and will bat
to open its rain-delayed cricket Test match with  England  in
Cardiff.  The match is scheduled to start at 2:45 p.m. local time,
but has been delayed by rain.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
